Entry - Class in fs.fibu2.data.model
This class represents an fsfibu2 journal entry.
Entry(String, float, Currency, GregorianCalendar, Category, String, HashMap<String, String>, String) - Constructor for class fs.fibu2.data.model.Entry
Creates an entry with values set to the given parameters
Entry(Node) - Constructor for class fs.fibu2.data.model.Entry
Expects a node containing the following subnodes (with appropriately formatted content):
- name (String)*
- value (float)*
- currency (A String containing the ISO 4217 code)*
- date (A date formatted as dd.MM.yyyy)*
- category (A node as described in Category)
- account (String, must be known to AccountLoader)*
- accountinformation (A node containing subnodes for each field id - named after that id - which contain the associated data as a string)
- additionalinformation (String)
